Hi there..

Once again Dr. Walther J. Veith gives a lecture that shows the Bible's accuracy. This time based upon archaeological findings and the history of Egypt. Some of the evidence is really quite amazing, like the title of these classes also suggest.

As always Dr. Veith is an excellent teacher; methodical and easy to follow. Most likely you'll be a bit wiser than before after following this lecture, or at least you'll have some more knowledge of the subject he teaches.
How you respond to it is of course the proof of how wise you've become.. :-)

